Epoz is a product for Zope/CMF

Epoz allows you to edit Zope- or Plone-objects with a wysiwyg-editor. No
plugins are required. You only have to use a recent browser (IE >= 5.5, Mozilla
>= 1.3.1, Netscape >= 7.1) that supports Rich-Text-controls (called Midas for
Mozilla).

WWW: http://www.zope.org/Members/mjablonski/Epoz

